Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.63,0:01:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,—Episode 007—\NMeeting The Big Four{NOTE:四天王の出会い}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.90,0:01:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.63,0:01:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.92,0:01:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For the first time, we've won a public game.{NOTE:私達は公開試合で始めての勝利を掴み。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone regained their confidence as if they were born anew.{NOTE:皆生まれ変わったように自身を取り戻した。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:01:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time.{NOTE:ほら、も一度。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.69,0:01:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Toss!{NOTE:トス。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I think our club has changed.{NOTE:おい、今までのバレー部とは違うと思うね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.29,0:02:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.34,0:02:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got our own first victory.{NOTE:XXX始めて勝ったんだもん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels different.{NOTE:今までとは違うのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.49,0:02:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.33,0:02:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, thank you.{NOTE:あ、サンキュー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,One more.{NOTE:もう一本。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Volleyball is about teamwork, right?{NOTE:皆、バレーはチームワークよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.77,0:02:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.{NOTE:そう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.25,0:02:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimi volleyball club's teamwork is the best in Japan.{NOTE:富士見学園バレー部のチームワークは日本一なんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My hunger's strong, too.{NOTE:XXXも強い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, girls.{NOTE:さ、皆。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.26,0:02:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The warm-up time is over.{NOTE:もうそろそろはXXXの終わる時間よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Hongou gets back soon.{NOTE:本郷先生がXXXるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the club room.{NOTE:さ、部室へ行きましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,– OK.\N– Let's go!{NOTE:—OK。\\N—それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,– Sorry, sorry.\N– Oh, it's Tsutomu-san.{NOTE:—ごめん、ごめん。\\N—ま、努さんじゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you in such a hurry?{NOTE:どうしたの、そんなに慌てて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Newspaper club has an emergency meeting.{NOTE:新聞部の緊急集会なんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.{NOTE:落ち着いてよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't suit a good newspaper club member such as yourself.{NOTE:そんなことじゃ優秀な新聞部員とは言えないわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the merge.{NOTE:合併。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.46,0:02:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're merging…!{NOTE:合併なんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.51,0:02:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Merging?{NOTE:合併?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's merging with whom?{NOTE:ま…一体何が？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The academy's upper management has a\hlot of problems. You heard about it too.{NOTE:学園の上に今まで色んな問題があったことは君達もう知ってるだろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of them stem out of the low student numbers.{NOTE:学園のXXXに比べて、生徒の数が少ないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with our tuition fees, the school recently cannot afford many expenses.{NOTE:つまり、授業料やそなたを場合にしても、色んな経費は掛かってやっていけない時代に来てんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So just now the board has decided that we'll merge with another school.{NOTE:それで今、職員会XX、合併することが発表されたんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.68,0:03:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who will we merge with?{NOTE:合併て、どんな学校と？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That I still don't know.{NOTE:や、それが分からない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm in a hurry. Bye.{NOTE:じゃ、急ぐから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because there's few students, the management goes bonkers.{NOTE:生徒の数が少ないから、経営が上手くいかないなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Municipal schools are going to the dogs.{NOTE:市立の学校何て情けないもんだよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What does merging mean?{NOTE:合併って？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It means joining with another school.{NOTE:他の学校と一緒に成ることよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that much.{NOTE:そんなことが分かってるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She's asking how it's going to look like.{NOTE:一緒成ってどう成るかってことよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really sure myself either.{NOTE:それはよく分かんないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When we merge, there will be no more Fujimi Academy, right?{NOTE:合併すると富士見学園じゃ無くなっちゃうでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's ridiculous.{NOTE:そーそんなバカな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine the school to\hdisappear. There's no way it'll happen.{NOTE:学校が無くなっちゃうなんとこと。あるはずないわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But the academy will certainly change.{NOTE:だけどさ、今までの学園とは違うものに成っちゃうだろうさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?{NOTE:お？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor!{NOTE:先生！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,– Professor!\N– Professor!{NOTE:—先生！\\N—先生！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true? The whole merging thing.{NOTE:本当なんですか？合併て言うのわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor, which school are we merging with?{NOTE:先生、どこの学校とか(XXX・結論)です？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not decided yet.{NOTE:それは未だ…決まってない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it mean Fujimi Academy will be no more?{NOTE:じゃ、富士見学園が無くなっちゃうの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That… that's still…{NOTE:そ…それは未だ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If that school has a volleyball club too,\Nwhat will happen to ours?{NOTE:その学校にもバレー部あるんだろうし、バレー部にどうなっちゃうんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The exact form of the merge…{NOTE:どう言う形で合併するか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.91,0:04:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,…is still undecided yet.{NOTE:それも未だ決まっていないだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:18.39,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Just when we've united, more troubles.{NOTE:折角纏まりかけた時に、又問題が…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happens now.{NOTE:どうなるかしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me.{NOTE:さ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it is, let it happen already.{NOTE:とんでもいいから、早くはっきりした欲しいわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean both the school and our club.{NOTE:学校とはどう成るか、バレー部どう成るのか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:えい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.{NOTE:ま。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,These girls…{NOTE:あの人達は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You. You're Fujimi Academy's volleyball club?{NOTE:あんたたち。富士見学園のバレー部ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct. What about it?{NOTE:そうよ。それはどうかしたの?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hahahaha.{NOTE:ハハハハハ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I presume you're from Hamaki Middle School.{NOTE:浜紀中学の人達ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in a volleyball club too, no?{NOTE:あなたたち…バレー部ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're in a volleyball club too, no?"{NOTE:「あなたたち…バレー部ね。」}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,…she says.{NOTE:だって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hahahaha.{NOTE:ハハハハ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, this is good.{NOTE:こいつは参った、がっくりね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My.{NOTE:ま。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know us?{NOTE:あたしたちを知らないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't blame you.{NOTE:無理ないわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You dropped out the first in the tournament.{NOTE:大会の第一試合で消えただったもん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.{NOTE:そうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes you the best losers, no?{NOTE:一番弱いことじゃない?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it.{NOTE:待ちなさいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, what now?{NOTE:あら、何か。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to beg us for a match now, are you.{NOTE:まさか「あたしたちと試合しよう」って言うんじゃないでしょうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hahahaha.{NOTE:ハハハハハ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,– Hold on—\N– Let her be, Kakko.{NOTE:—ちょっと。\\N—止しなさい、カッコ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Hamaki…{NOTE:選手権大会で浜紀中学は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.17,0:05:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,…was placed second in the tournament.{NOTE:…準優勝だったわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Katsuragi-san.{NOTE:桂城さんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the deal with these girls?{NOTE:何があったの、あの人達と？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing particular.{NOTE:いいえ、別に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:05:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know these girls?{NOTE:あの人達を知っている？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No.{NOTE:いいえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's those four.{NOTE:あの四人よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They advanced from an\hunknown school to the finals…{NOTE:無名の学校優勝決定まで進めて、}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,…and quickly gained fame as Hamaki volleyball club's "Big Four".{NOTE:一躍有名にした浜紀中学バレー部の四天王と言うのわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"Big Four"?{NOTE:四天王？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So they're the Hamaki's Big Four…{NOTE:あれが浜紀中学の四天王なの…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard rumors about them.{NOTE:噂には聞いてたは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Their attack duo is famed to be excellent.{NOTE:あの四人のコンビ攻撃は素晴らしいって評判ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When we don't know what will happen to our school…{NOTE:学園はどう成っちゃう分からないなんて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.77,0:06:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like practicing much.{NOTE:こんな気分じゃ、練習もうできないわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't take breaks from the practice.{NOTE:練習休まXXいけないわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, captain?{NOTE:ね、キャプテン？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!{NOTE:キャプテン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Trouble!{NOTE:大変よ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?{NOTE:なによ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They decided who will be merging with.{NOTE:合併の相手が決まったんだって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Hamaki Middle School.{NOTE:XXXとか浜紀中学と合併するんだってさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamaki?{NOTE:浜紀中学と？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.{NOTE:そう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamaki is coming to us.{NOTE:浜紀中学とこっちをつってくるんですってさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the club?{NOTE:じゃ、バレー部は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Big Four comes to us too.{NOTE:あの四天王と一緒に成るのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.{NOTE:そう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho.{NOTE:よいっしょ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, good.{NOTE:さ、良いわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're late.{NOTE:ほら、遅刻よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.{NOTE:ごめん、ごめん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Katsuragi-san's not coming to practice today.{NOTE:あのね、桂城さん今日練習できないって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a preparatory meeting before the graduation ceremony.{NOTE:卒業式なんても、XXXの感じXXX打ち合わせるんだって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Graduation, huh…{NOTE:もうすぐ卒業式ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be lonely without Katsuragi-san.{NOTE:桂城さんはいなくなると寂しく成るわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange, we'll have Hamaki's Big Four join us.{NOTE:その代わりに入ってくるのは浜紀中学の四天王なんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.56,0:07:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll get tough.{NOTE:厳しくなるわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, also, professor Hongou…{NOTE:あ、それから本郷先生…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,…since it seemed that the teachers meeting will prolong…{NOTE:職員会は長く成りそうだから…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.13,0:07:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,…he told us to start by ourselves.{NOTE:練習を始めておくよう言って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then, let's begin.{NOTE:じゃ、始めるわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go at it with full power.{NOTE:張り切って行こう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't lose to Hamaki's Big Four.{NOTE:浜紀中学の四天王何かに負けないようにさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We won't lose.{NOTE:おう。負けてたまるもんか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to these girls.{NOTE:こんな四天王XXXさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight.{NOTE:はい、ファイト。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,One more!{NOTE:じゃ、もう一本。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:07:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The Big Four?{NOTE:し…四天王？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain.{NOTE:キャプテン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here.{NOTE:来た。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So-so, I guess.{NOTE:ままじゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Equipment looks new too.{NOTE:XXXは新しそうだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a better gym that I expected.{NOTE:思ったより、良い体育館ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be able to practice here.{NOTE:これなら、十分練習できるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to try it out already.{NOTE:中々(XXX・いかして)(XXX・見じゃん)。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I doubt this place has seen much action anyway.{NOTE:どうかのチームじゃXXXされて所へよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, they're the Hamaki's Big Four?{NOTE:ね、あれは浜紀中の四天王なの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If we practice here, the gym might become amazing too.{NOTE:あたしたちが使ってればこの体育館も本望ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.{NOTE:そうそう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.{NOTE:よし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyouko.{NOTE:敬子。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.{NOTE:待って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Fujimi Academy volleyball club's captain, Ayuhara Kozue.{NOTE:富士見学園バレー部キャプテン。鮎原こずえです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We've met before, but…{NOTE:いつかどっかであったようだけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,…let's have a proper introduction.{NOTE:…改めて、御挨拶するわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:09:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hamaki's captain. Izumi Yuri.{NOTE:あたしは浜紀中キャプテンの、泉ゆり。\\Nいずみ・ゆり}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kudou Keiko-chan.{NOTE:工藤圭子ちゃん。\\Nくどう・けいこ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozawa Yukie.{NOTE:小沢幸江。\\Nおざわ・ゆきえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Katori Yoshiko.{NOTE:香取良子。\\Nかとり・よしこ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.51,0:09:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people apparently call\hus The Big Four of Hamaki.{NOTE:あたしたちのこと浜紀中の四天王だ何て言う人もいるようね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hahahaha.{NOTE:ハハハハ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.85,0:09:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We came to see if we could practice here.{NOTE:(XXX・大学から)、あたしたちもここで練習すること成ったんで見にきたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're merging, we're in the same club, right.{NOTE:学校が合併されたら、同じバレー部ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's work together.{NOTE:よろしく。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well…{NOTE:さ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really sure if we'll be able to work together.{NOTE:そう言われても、あんたたちのためによろしくできるかどうか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?{NOTE:どう言うことなの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Our volleyball is intense.{NOTE:あたしたちのバレーは厳しいのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. There you have it.{NOTE:ん。そう言うこと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt you'll keep up.{NOTE:あんたたちに付いてこれない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?{NOTE:なー何だって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it again!{NOTE:ちょっと。もう一度言ってごらんよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Naka.{NOTE:ナカ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll practice in our own way.{NOTE:私達のやり方でやくからさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep up with us, good.{NOTE:付いてこれる人は付いてくれば良いじゃん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.19,0:09:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph. After merging with us, you're part\hof Fujimi's volleyball club, aren't you.{NOTE:フン。合併されたら、あなたたちも富士見学園のバレー部でしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You should obey captain Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:だったら、キャプテン鮎原さんのXXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.{NOTE:それは無理ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, the difference in our skills is too vast.{NOTE:だって、あたしたちあんたたちじゃ、実力は違いすぎるもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you picking a fight?{NOTE:喧嘩おる気なの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.{NOTE:待ってよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's crazy.{NOTE:皆XXXバカにされて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait.{NOTE:待って、待って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it already.{NOTE:皆、辞めて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't graduate with a\hpeace of\hmind in such a mess.{NOTE:こんなことじゃあたし、安心した卒業していけないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't merging mean we get to be friends with each other?{NOTE:皆、合併して一緒なる仲間のはずじゃないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a third year student, Katsuragi Imi. What is going on?{NOTE:あたし三年の桂城由美。いったいどうしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't intend to pick a fight with you guys.{NOTE:あたしたちは別に喧嘩なんかするつむりないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that we become a\hsingle club after the merge.{NOTE:合併すれば、それは確かに一つのバレー部よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do our best as the club's members.{NOTE:学園のバレー部として、頑張るわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can do volleyball in our own way only.{NOTE:でも、あたしたちはあたしたちのバレーしかできないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,– In our…\N– …own way only?{NOTE:—あたしたち…\\N—あたしたちのバレー？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,– Let's head back.\N– Bye.{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi-san, I apologize.{NOTE:桂城さん、ごめんなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised.{NOTE:驚いたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.37,0:10:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You were looking daggers so much.{NOTE:皆睨み合ってすごいんだもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be difficult, all right. But I urge you.{NOTE:最終は色々難しいこともあるでしょう。けど、皆、お願いね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make a good club with them.{NOTE:立派なバレー部にXXXってね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That way I'll graduate with no regrets.{NOTE:安心して卒業していけるように。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.{NOTE:おねがいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:58.76,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1200,0)}35th graduation ceremony of Fujimi Academy Middle School{NOTE:富士見学園中学校第３５回卒業式会場}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.{NOTE:では、無事卒業…おめでとう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.45,0:11:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, sir.{NOTE:有り難う御座います。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi-san, congratulations.{NOTE:桂城さん、卒業おめでとう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.{NOTE:あいがとう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect the club's tradition with everyone.{NOTE:皆でバレー部の伝統守ってね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.{NOTE:おねがいね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a great, strong team.{NOTE:ちゃんとXXXして、強いチームを作ってね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The club's safe in my hands.{NOTE:大丈夫です。任しておいてください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi-san will probably join Fujimi high school volleyball club.{NOTE:桂城さんは…富士見高校のバレー部に入るのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll join it next year too.{NOTE:あたしも来年は入るわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.{NOTE:あたしもよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to do our best.{NOTE:頑張らなきゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to do our best…{NOTE:頑張らなきゃ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?{NOTE:あれは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.79,0:11:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our girls university's club.{NOTE:富士見女子大のバレー部よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, awesome.{NOTE:あ、すごい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing training.{NOTE:すごい練習ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Their team once won the All-Japan tournament.{NOTE:全国大会に優勝したことがあるチームですもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.21,0:11:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,– Wanna try?\N– Yeah.{NOTE:—行ってみない？\\N—え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.14,0:11:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:—おい。\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:11:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right at you, sweetie.{NOTE:あ、ちびっこ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got what it takes, sweeties.{NOTE:ちびちゃん達。やるわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimi Academy, right?{NOTE:富士見学園ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Ayuhara Kozue of the volleyball club.{NOTE:バレー部の鮎原こずえです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hayakawa Midori.{NOTE:早川みどりです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm their captain, Oohara Mari.{NOTE:キャプテンの大原まりよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.{NOTE:すごい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You both have very good qualities.{NOTE:二人共とてもいい素質を持ってるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna play with us for a while?{NOTE:どう？よかったら、すこしやってみる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,– Please treat us well.\N– Please treat us well.{NOTE:—よろしくおねがいします。\\N—よろしくおねがいします。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're ready.{NOTE:—おねがいします。\\N—おねがいします。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I won't hold back.{NOTE:いい？手加減しないわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Trouble.{NOTE:大変だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Spring break started this morning. What are your plans?{NOTE:ね、明後日から春休みけど、どうするの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.{NOTE:んん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I still haven't decided anything.{NOTE:未だ何も計画を立てていないの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you be going home, to Tōkyō?{NOTE:東京の家に帰るでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.{NOTE:そうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, got an idea.{NOTE:そうだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk to Oohara-san and practice with them.{NOTE:大原さんのチームにXXXもらって、練習をしよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,With university girls?{NOTE:大学のチームに？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Will she let us?{NOTE:やってくれるかしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to ask—{NOTE:さ、それは頼んでみなきゃ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!{NOTE:キャプテン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, trouble. Serious trouble with the club!{NOTE:キャプテン。一大事！バレー部の一大事よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you flustered?{NOTE:どうしたの、そんなに慌てて？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"Serious trouble"… Ofuku, you always make fuss over most mundane things.{NOTE:一大事じゃなんて、おフクにいつもXXXなんだから…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?{NOTE:なに言ってんの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If this isn't serious, I don't know what is.{NOTE:これが一大事と言うはなくて、何が一大事なの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They occupied the gym.{NOTE:乗り込んできたの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They're practicing now.{NOTE:練習してるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hamaki's Big Four…{NOTE:浜紀中の四天王が…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,– Eh?\N– Eh?{NOTE:—え？\\N—え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.96,0:13:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Hamaki came here, they said they can't use the city gym anymore.{NOTE:浜紀中学は立ち退いたのに、市のスポーツセンターができるんだって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And now that the other gym is under renovation…{NOTE:それで(XXX・グランで)何かの工事がもう始まっていて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,…they got nowhere to practice.{NOTE:練習する場所は無くなっちゃったら死んだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they went to us…{NOTE:だからこっちに行ったとわけなんだけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But their practice is awful.{NOTE:その練習は酷いのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They act as if they owned the place.{NOTE:もう丸で自分達だけのコート見たいにしてさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Kakko and Naka?{NOTE:カッコやナカ達は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They promised not to fight until Katsuragi-san graduates.{NOTE:桂城さんの卒業する時、絶対に喧嘩しないって誓ったでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Until now they were patient.{NOTE:だからじっと我慢してるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no telling what they do now. Let's hurry.{NOTE:でもいつまでもXXX分からない。早く。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, captain.{NOTE:あ、キャプテン、大変！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that.{NOTE:あれ見てよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:おい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:良い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:—それじゃ。\\N—おおおお。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Our court…{NOTE:あたしたちのコート…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Come at me.{NOTE:しまってくれ(は良い・よい)。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Big Four, my foot.{NOTE:なにが四天王よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How arrogant!{NOTE:生意気ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Naka.{NOTE:待って、ナカ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.86,0:14:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-san, let's practice together.{NOTE:泉さん。皆で一緒に練習しましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still in the middle of the training.{NOTE:未だあたしたちの練習は終わってないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait there for a bit.{NOTE:そこで待てって、ちょっと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is everyone's court.{NOTE:ここは皆のコートよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay if we all do it, right?{NOTE:皆で一緒にやればいいでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh.{NOTE:ヘ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting in our way.{NOTE:邪魔なんだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You just don't get it.{NOTE:分かんないだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If we practice with you, you'll only hinder us.{NOTE:あんたたち一緒ことよ邪魔なんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.{NOTE:ま。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:14:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're free, go fetch a ball or something.{NOTE:暇だったら、球拾いでもしてよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:14:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fitting for you.{NOTE:その方がお似合いよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.{NOTE:そうそう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.82,0:15:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all good girls after all.{NOTE:ね？皆良い子ちゃん、だからさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hahahaha.{NOTE:ハハハハハ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Midori-san.{NOTE:ああ、みどりさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you did it.{NOTE:やったわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna fight, we'll fight.{NOTE:喧嘩なら、相手なるよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. How shameless.{NOTE:畜生。XXXなって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Midori-san, what did you do…{NOTE:みどりさん、何てこと…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to stay silent when they make fun of us?{NOTE:だって…こんなにXXXだって、黙ってるつもり？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't intend to.{NOTE:黙ってするつもりはないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do want to fight us.{NOTE:喧嘩しようと言うの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. It can't be helped.{NOTE:こうなったら、仕方ないわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.06,0:15:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No.{NOTE:いいえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll settle it with this ball.{NOTE:このボールで決めるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, how interesting.{NOTE:え？それは面白いわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll finally figure who's stronger, no buts.{NOTE:これでどっちに力があるか、はっきりするわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do a four players match.{NOTE:四人制で勝負しましょうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how it works?{NOTE:四人制って、あんたたちは知ってる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look down on us!{NOTE:バカにしないで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a system often used for training by Russian teams.{NOTE:ソ連の選手がよく練習に使うだとことぐらいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.57,0:15:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that much, okay!?{NOTE:バレーだって、知ってるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.{NOTE:それは結構ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start.{NOTE:じゃ、始めましょうか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it's not very challenging if it is you who challenge us.{NOTE:あたしたち四天王に、挑戦するなんか、あんなで履行じゃないね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll win with these arrogant missies.{NOTE:あの高慢な花を必勝ってやるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.57,0:16:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You girls.{NOTE:よ、君達。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be your referee.{NOTE:私が審判をしよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Kajioka.{NOTE:梶岡先生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hamaki volleyball club's coach, Kajioka. Nice to meet you.{NOTE:私は浜紀中学バレー部のコーチをしてる、梶岡だ。よろしく。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,After the merge, looks like I'll take care of you too.{NOTE:合併したら、私は君達の面倒を見ることなるだろうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have professor Hongou.{NOTE:でも、あたしたちには本郷先生が…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I led Hamaki's team to the championship finals.{NOTE:私は浜紀中学のチームを育てて、優勝決定戦まで行った。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural that I become your coach as well.{NOTE:新しいチームのコーチも、当然私が引き受ける。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,When was that decided?{NOTE:それはいつ決まったんですか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,– Ah, professor!\N– Professor!{NOTE:—あ、先生！\\N—先生！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hongou.{NOTE:本郷です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. I'm Kajioka.{NOTE:では…梶岡です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Err… it wasn't decided, but that's not to say it couldn't happen.{NOTE:じゃ…決まったって言うわけじゃないんだが、そうなるかもしれないって言うことでしてね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Good that I called him over, right?{NOTE:先生を呼んできたの方がよかったでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I filled him with the details.{NOTE:今までのことは皆話しておいたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're holding a game, no? Good luck.{NOTE:勝負するのね。頑張ってね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you said it, I want to see the\hstrength of professor Hongou's team.{NOTE:ま、そう言うことで、本郷先生のチームの力を見ておきたいと思いましてね、}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But… about refereeing…{NOTE:でも、あの…審判は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it all right if I do it?{NOTE:私がやってもいいですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.{NOTE:どうぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:16:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor, how many years have you been coaching volleyball?{NOTE:先生、あの…バレーは…コーチを何年ぐらいXXX?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I started only recently.{NOTE:いいえ。本校に来て、始めてばかりです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? I've been coaching for five years already.{NOTE:そうですか。私もう五年に成りますかね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How spiteful.{NOTE:嫌らしいなね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, decide the serve.{NOTE:じゃ、サーブ権を決めなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,– Rock, paper.\N– Rock, paper.{NOTE:—じゃんけん。\\N—じゃんけん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll serve first.{NOTE:こっちのサーブね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin the match.{NOTE:試合開始。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!{NOTE:頑張って！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Show them!{NOTE:(XXX・先生)!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go.{NOTE:行くわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.98,0:17:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!{NOTE:おう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.{NOTE:任して！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind, don't mind!{NOTE:ドンマイドンマイ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.{NOTE:ごめん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:55.40,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen such a curve ball before.{NOTE:始めて見たわ、あんな変化球。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:17:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep this pace.{NOTE:この(XXX・バッチ)にいただきましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull yourself together.{NOTE:しっかりね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes!{NOTE:(XXX・プレー)よ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Midori!{NOTE:みどり！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice going, nice going. We'll end it in to time.{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!{NOTE:キャプテン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow.{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't strain yourself, now.{NOTE:XXXないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How cute.{NOTE:(XXX・軽い、軽い・華麗、華麗)！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:39.76,Alternative,,0,0,0,,They're on a different level.{NOTE:はるかに力が違う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:41.13,Alternative,,0,0,0,,We might lose.{NOTE:負けるかもしれない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:51.81,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara.{NOTE:鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:52.52,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Good luck.{NOTE:頑張れ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:54.28,Alternative,,0,0,0,,You know how to work until the end.{NOTE:出きるところまでやるんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:56.91,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Me and you girls started it together.{NOTE:君達と私は一緒にバレーを始めた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:59.07,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Fight with all you have.{NOTE:どこまでできるか戦って行こう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:00.09,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Do your best!{NOTE:頑張るんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:00.73,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara.{NOTE:鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.94,0:19:02.50,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.{NOTE:やるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.61,0:19:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain.{NOTE:キャプテン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it.{NOTE:頑張るのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on, come on.{NOTE:さ、さ、さ、さ、さ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it together.{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Too weak!{NOTE:(XXX・軽い、軽い・華麗、華麗)。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's win and get the gym already.{NOTE:XXXセットXXXもいただきましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?{NOTE:どうしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.{NOTE:以上。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,– Hey!\N– Nice.{NOTE:—おい！\\N—いいな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:19:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, it hurts.{NOTE:あ、痛い…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.21,0:20:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get the serve back.{NOTE:いただきましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Chance, chance, chance!{NOTE:チャンス、チャンス、チャンス。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.42,0:20:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,One more point and it's over.{NOTE:あと一点でお終いよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:33.20,Alternative,,0,0,0,,No good.{NOTE:いかん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.91,0:20:38.47,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Fufufu.{NOTE:ふふふ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.02,0:20:40.70,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Do you understand our power now?{NOTE:あたしたちの力を分かったでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming!{NOTE:あ、来るよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!{NOTE:キャプテン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.65,0:20:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it? No more complaints, I hope?{NOTE:どう？問題じゃないわね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we won't be seeing you in the finals.{NOTE:(XXX・前半戦)に成らないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Too easy.{NOTE:ね…大変ないわ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:00.76,Alternative,,0,0,0,,We lost.{NOTE:負けた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:01.71,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Complete defeat.{NOTE:完敗だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:03.71,Alternative,,0,0,0,,But we can start again.{NOTE:だが、未だ一緒に初めよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:06.35,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Move on to the next goal, acquire new strength.{NOTE:次の目標に…新しい力に向かって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara.{NOTE:鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be coaching you.{NOTE:君達のコーチはこの私はする。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, the match's over.{NOTE:さ、試合終了だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well.{NOTE:よくやった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We can start a new club here, right?{NOTE:あたしたちが新しいバレー部を作ってけばいいわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best.{NOTE:頑張ろうよ。ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.18,0:21:46.01,Alternative,,0,0,0,,How vexing.{NOTE:悔しい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.37,0:21:47.36,Alternative,,0,0,0,,It's vexing, but…{NOTE:悔しいけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:48.94,Alternative,,0,0,0,,We lost through and through.{NOTE:あたしたちは負けたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.31,0:21:53.32,Alternative,,0,0,0,,We lost it…{NOTE:負けたのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.76,0:21:55.55,Alternative,,0,0,0,,For our power to be so different…{NOTE:XXX力が違う何て…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.49,0:22:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't step back.{NOTE:あたしはやる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.77,0:22:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll surely show them.{NOTE:きっとやってみせるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you going so soon?{NOTE:あら、もう行くの?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.28,0:22:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The spring break has just started.{NOTE:折角の春休みだって言うのに…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.59,0:22:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't take no for an answer.{NOTE:言い出したら、聞かないんだから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.09,0:22:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,– Take care.\N{はい。}– Yes, auntie.{NOTE:気を付けてね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you need anything, call me.{NOTE:欲しいものあったら、電話してね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Be safe.{NOTE:じゃ、行ってらっしゃい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.27,0:22:30.20,Alternative,,0,0,0,,It's first time I go to a training camp.{NOTE:合宿なんて始めてだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.20,0:22:33.35,Alternative,,0,0,0,,On top of it, it's an university training camp. It must be tough.{NOTE:それも、大学のバレー部の合宿なんて…すごく厳しいだろうな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.17,0:22:48.31,Alternative,,0,0,0,,How annoying.{NOTE:悔しい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.49,0:22:51.27,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I won't lose to The Big Four.{NOTE:四天王になんか負けるもんか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.63,0:22:53.69,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I'll attain new power without fail.{NOTE:なんとしても、実力を付けて帰るわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:22:59.14,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Now that I got a special\hpermission from the captain Oohara…{NOTE:キャプテン大原さん特別に許可をいただいたんだ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.14,0:22:59.88,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I'll give it a go.{NOTE:やってみる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:02.98,Alternative,,0,0,0,,How far can I go?{NOTE:自分のバレーがどこまでできるか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.98,0:23:03.87,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I'll find out.{NOTE:やってみるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.46,0:23:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem.{NOTE:ゴホン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this seat free?{NOTE:この席は開いてますか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.{NOTE:どうぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.46,0:23:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Fufu.{NOTE:ふふ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.26,0:23:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Midori-san!{NOTE:ま、みどりさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.13,0:23:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going too.{NOTE:あたしも行くわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,To the university training camp, that is.{NOTE:大学の合宿にね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.35,0:23:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?{NOTE:ま…どうして分かったの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.59,0:23:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy.{NOTE:分かるわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.66,0:23:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You had that "what should I do" look.{NOTE:鮎原さんは「何をしよう」とする勘ぐられば。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.06,0:23:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I called captain Oohara-san, too.{NOTE:あたしもキャプテン大原さんに電話をして頼むんだのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.06,0:23:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She told me about your request.{NOTE:「鮎原さんは電話した」直ぐアウトだったそうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.71,0:23:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then your aunt disclosed the departure time.{NOTE:そうして、電車の時間は叔母様から。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Midori-san.{NOTE:みどりさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, let's fight together.{NOTE:鮎原さん、一緒にやりましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.59,0:23:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how tough it'll be.{NOTE:どんなに厳しい合宿でも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.25,0:23:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:23:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll fight.{NOTE:やるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.42,0:23:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show them how to play.{NOTE:あたしはきっとやってみせるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.65,0:23:56.85,Alternative,,0,0,0,,While Izumi Yuri's curve ball technique remains a secret…{NOTE:泉ユリの変化球サーブXXXを胸に秘め(る)。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.85,0:24:02.44,Alternative,,0,0,0,,…Kozue-Midori attack duo participates in Fujimi all-girls university volleyball training camp.{NOTE:こずえ・みどりアタックコンビは富士見大学女子バレー部の合宿に参加した。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.44,0:24:05.87,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Captain Oohara, seeing through their goal right away…{NOTE:彼女XX目的はなんであると見抜いたキャプテンの大原は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.87,0:24:08.89,Alternative,,0,0,0,,…doesn't go easy, even though they're middle schoolers.{NOTE:中学生といえども、容赦無くXXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.89,0:24:11.58,Alternative,,0,0,0,,About to collapse, they get reprimanded by Oohara.{NOTE:挫けそうに成る二人に大原の叱責はとる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.23,0:24:15.26,Alternative,,0,0,0,,But they endure the training desperately.{NOTE:だが、二人は練習に必死に耐える。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.26,0:24:18.63,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Finally, they start seeing through the curve ball.{NOTE:ついに、変化球サーブXXXの飛球を身につけるだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.63,0:24:21.95,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Please look forward to the next episode.{NOTE:さ、来週のアタックナンバーワンをお楽しみに。}
